Motormaster looks to Stratus who just entered Astroblast. He could feel
them pulling away from earth. He received Squawktalk's transmission. "I'm
not sure what you should do, tell me what you see there" he said calmly. He
looked to the new Decepticon. "How did you arrive on earth?" He questions
Stratus.
